{"tid":1635581,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中美貿談前景再現不明朗 道指早段跌逾百點","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:53:05.000Z","uid":7828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e24b8549cdcfd4eb1a7bb3910fddf6655488fed","tid":1635581,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"中美高級別貿易談判前景再現不明朗，道指早段跌逾百點。<br />\n<br />\n截至本港時間晚上約9時40分，道指報26464點，跌108點或0.41%；標普500指數報2939點，跌12點或0.42%；納指報7953點，跌30點或0.38%。<br />\n<br />\n中美兩國貿易談判代表周四舉行高級別會議，外電報道，中國官員預期，雙方很難在達成全面性協議方面有進展。根據報道，中方首席談判代表、國務院副總理劉鶴向代表團成員表明，他提出的建議將不包括承諾經濟體制改革去消除對行業的補助，而這是華府一直在談判時的主要要求。<br />\n<br />\n油價上升，紐約原油期貨現時每桶報53.39美元，升0.58美元或1.1%；倫敦布蘭特期油報58.87美元，升0.5美元或0.86%。"},{"pid":"1cb6ca1ab036af41231d355d2bc02a89bddb137b","tid":1635581,"uid":308915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"其實根本冇可能會傾得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8bbadedbb3a9a218e5f5916fbb2ae46b71f5cb","tid":1635581,"uid":315798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"希望傾唔成"},{"pid":"af0425068d82ecaa88f78458887bb093b603f3cf","tid":1635581,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民撳爆總行 atm 換美金保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行call loan 然後支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d8b2bc98ab54f3471a0807e2b8ef2e849dfde20e","tid":1635581,"uid":186543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"聽日點都係必跌啦，緊急法"},{"pid":"f73cdfb7b388cd2d646b301bd692e8bb004d6d25","tid":1635581,"uid":45727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:53:05.000Z"